THIS VERSION
============                                                 

V3.0 - Written in AMOS 1.3 - 8/6/98 (Totally re-written)    

So whats new in the latest version of this arcade classic?   

This game is getting a bit long in the tooth now but I still 
wasn't happy with it. The problem was mainly with the speed. 
The previous versions were playable on a bog standard A1200  
but when it came to an A500 it looked pretty pathetic. This  
version was written and compiled on an A500 so I could       
seriously optimize the code so that it would run at a decent 
frame rate. The result is that it now runs at a very         
impressive speed indeed. Other improvements include faster
collision detection, improved joystick detection, better
sound FX and a better screen display.                                                     


HOW TO PLAY
===========                                                  
                                                             
