A500 OWNERS                                                  
===========                                                  
                                                             
If you only have 512k in your A500 then the game will not work.
If you have a 1/2 Meg upgrade though, all will be fine.
                                                         
                                                             
Tested on A500 (1 Meg)                                       
          A500+                                              
          A600                                               
          A1200                                              
          A1200 + 030                                        
          A1200 + 040                                        
          A1200 + 060                                        
                                                             
060 owners may experience strange sound effects from time to
time.  This is no fault of mine, I think its due to the way AMOS
plays raw samples.  The actual game runs fine though.             


BUGS
====

There are a couple of small bugs in the game that I know about and
are associated with collision checks on the green bases.  Sometimes
a bomb or your missile won't detect the base properly and will
result in them passing straight through the base.  This vary rarely
happens though and doesn't spoil the playability of the game at all.
If you find any other bugs, please let me know and I will do my best
to correct them.


